originalText.text:
I was recommended to Kiambu through the head administrator at Erik Dalton’s Freedom from Pain Institute. It is one of the Premier Educational Outlets for well trained, experienced Massage Therapists to enhance their skills to the highest level in our field.
She told me that Kiambu was one of their Master Massage Therapists and that he had assisted many of classes taught after his certification, as well. Highest recommendation!
I have been a Massage Therapist for 35 years now, and Kiambu is the best therapist I’ve ever worked with. Extremely professional, and I trust him comp. You should, as well.
I have sent a couple of my most challenging clients to him for assistance, and it has been a good call for all of us.
I give Kiambu my highest recommendation.
